00:57:47,080 --> 00:57:53,800
is a workshop. I do a lot of printmaking. I went 
to college at a school that was very focused on  

623
00:57:53,800 --> 00:57:59,560
interdisciplinary work, and I feel like I bring 
a lot of manual analog processes into my work a  

