01:02:16,720 --> 01:02:25,360
at Meta on GenAI stuff. He's a director on the 
GenAI team at Meta and is very bought into AI  

673
01:02:25,360 --> 01:02:30,560
as a whole thing. I am a little [inaudible 
01:02:28] about its impact on a lot of the  

674
01:02:30,560 --> 01:02:34,920
things that we do. I think, overall, it 
will become a tool and be very useful,  

675
01:02:34,920 --> 01:02:41,000
especially in a lot of different fields. But I 
think this timeframe in which it's more novelty  

676
01:02:41,000 --> 01:02:47,360
