01:03:26,760 --> 01:03:31,760
I could see the validity of that in the creative 
iterative process. I think the biggest thing for  

684
01:03:31,760 --> 01:03:42,840
me is that I find that the sloggy, slow dregs of 
work is very fulfilling to me, that a lot of the  

685
01:03:42,840 --> 01:03:49,480
evangelists of AI are like, "Oh, imagine if you 
