always ahead of the game. The second that she 
could read, she was like, "Oh, picture books  

728
01:07:42,280 --> 01:07:47,880
are for babies." Now she's reading, she goes 
into Pegasus books and is just like, "Where  

729
01:07:47,880 --> 01:07:52,640
