796
01:13:34,440 --> 01:13:38,720
come back to share with folks, 
find useful, and work your life?

797
01:13:38,720 --> 01:13:43,160
It's funny being a lettering artist because 
I'm not much of a quotes gal, all things  

798
01:13:43,160 --> 01:13:48,480
considered. I should be because I could make 
a million dollars by just making "live, laugh,  

799
01:13:48,480 --> 01:13:55,440
love" pillows or whatever, but I am not usually 
