what they do and that that's why I want to work  

836
01:17:24,960 --> 01:17:31,200
with them. With the house, I definitely 
had opinions about stuff. But in general,  

837
01:17:31,200 --> 01:17:35,880
I'm just like, "Hey, this is your thing. You're 
the expert. What do you think? Let me give you the  

838
01:17:35,880 --> 01:17:43,000
parameters and the things that we have to think 
about. Because you know more about wood resources,  

839
01:17:43,000 --> 01:17:49,200
and you know more about the cabinet spacing, and 
whatever, you tell me what you think is going to  

840
01:17:49,200 --> 01:17:54,200
work best based on all these things that I 
laid out for you." I found it to be quite  

841
01:17:54,200 --> 01:18:00,880
easy. I only got really wigged out about 
