851
01:18:45,680 --> 01:18:51,200
do that. And I think that that permeates through 
everything that I do in my life. It definitely is  

852
01:18:51,200 --> 01:18:57,600
a huge part of the logo work, because you really 
can do anything when it comes to typography. 

853
01:18:57,600 --> 01:19:03,640
It can go in 50 million directions. It's just 
about having someone tell you, "Yes, we could take  

854
01:19:03,640 --> 01:19:09,480
